{"tid":311244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女醫生免費服務吸客遭同行投訴 醫委會裁定專業失德罪成","createTime":"2017-07-06T12:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T19:37:26.000Z","uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2506e4d247183dd564708b222f150e665d60ddd6","tid":311244,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"一名女西醫因透過免費提供血糖測試、流感疫苗注射度血壓等服務，並藉此招徠生意，遭醫委會裁定專業失德罪成，判處停牌1個月，緩刑1年。<br />\n<br />\n被控的女西醫盧燕玲於2002年取得執業資格，曾在醫管局工作4年，之後受聘於鰂魚涌東匯中心一間診所。她被指在2013年9月至12月期間，於診所內透過免費提供服務作招徠，醫委會同年12月3日收到另一名在同一大廈開診所的醫生投訴，指控她的診所內有一些展板及電子器材，並標榜可以免費提供血糖測試，流感疫苗注射、血壓量度等服務。<br />\n<br />\n醫委會主席劉允怡認為，雖然盧只是受僱，但有責任提醒僱主不可以用這種方式招徠生意，因為醫生有責任確保診所不可以有任何形式的廣告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170704&amp;guid=56911248&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170704%26guid%3D56911248%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=1Yex6I4Ej0n%2FmToe9nq7BJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=76afb593\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170704%26guid%3D56911248%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=1864a1ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170704&amp;guid=56911248&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"8012230cc5fa9908feee7135f1dc9c655461627d","tid":311244,"uid":78165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f6bb0570cde86cd72be49b682dded3caae8bbb","tid":311244,"uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"以為免費性服務"},{"pid":"5d9ae3661c0eb4f9be207e960c46970dafc3745d","tid":311244,"uid":26451,"like":95,"dislike":7,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5805333a417b3